<p>Silver Spring's Cold-Mixed climate demands versatile HVAC systems capable of handling both sweltering summers with temperatures reaching the 90s and cold winters that can dip below freezing. For optimal efficiency, homeowners should consider high-efficiency heat pumps with SEER ratings of 16-20 and HSPF ratings of 9.5 or higher. These systems excel in moderate climates like Silver Spring, providing both heating and cooling while maintaining energy efficiency year-round.</p>

