<p>Consider seasonal installation timing - HVAC upgrades are best completed during spring or fall when systems aren't in peak demand, while solar installations can proceed year-round but may face weather delays during winter months. Many Silver Spring homeowners benefit from energy audits before making major investments, identifying air sealing, insulation, and window upgrade opportunities that reduce overall energy needs and improve both solar and HVAC system performance.</p>

